article.description: Terrell Brown registered 19 points as New Mexico State beat Texas Rio Grande Valley 79-72 in the Western Athletic Conference Tourney semifinals on Friday night.
article.headline: New Mexico St. beats Texas Rio Grande Valley 79-72
article.linkText: New Mexico St. beats Texas Rio Grande Valley 79-72
article.story: LAS VEGAS -- Terrell Brown registered 19 points as New Mexico State beat Texas Rio Grande Valley 79-72 in the Western Athletic Conference Tourney semifinals on Friday night. AJ Harris had 15 points for New Mexico State (29-4). Clayton Henry added 12 points. Eli Chuha had seven rebounds for New Mexico State. Tyson Smith scored a career-high 23 points for the Vaqueros (19-16). Lesley Varner II added 15 points.
